OL,3,CPolice and crime commissioners to be
OL,4,Cscrapped
OL,6,FInstead, mayors and council leaders
OL,7,Fwill take up the responsibilities of
OL,8,Fpolicing arrangements.
OL,10,FPolicing minister Sarah Jones
OL,11,Fannounced the move in the Commons on
OL,12,FThursday.
OL,14,FIn a statement, Home Secretary Shabana
OL,15,FMahmood said: "The introduction of
OL,16,FPolice and Crime Commissioners by the
OL,17,Flast government was a failed
OL,18,Fexperiment.
