OL,6,F"I will introduce new reforms so
OL,7,Fpolice are accountable to their local
OL,8,Fmayoralties or local councils.
OL,10,F"The savings will fund more
OL,11,Fneighbourhood police on the beat
OL,12,Facross the country, fighting crime and
OL,13,Fprotecting our communities."
OL,15,FShadow Home Secretary Chris Philp
OL,16,Fcalled the move "tinkering around the
OL,17,Fedges from a government which is
OL,18,Ffailing on crime and policing."
