OL,6,FHe accused the government of "simply
OL,7,Frearranging the deck chairs on the
OL,8,FTitanic".
OL,10,FPhilp warned of the changes removing a
OL,11,F"directly elected official" and
OL,12,Freplacing them with a "faceless
OL,13,Fcommittee of local bureaucrats".
OL,15,FReacting to the expected announcement,
OL,16,FAssociation of Police and Crime
OL,17,FCommissioners (APCC) chairwoman Emily
OL,18,FSpurrell said the body is "deeply
OL,19,Fdisappointed by this decision and the
OL,20,Flack of engagement with us".
