OL,6,FShe warned: "Abolishing PCCs now,
OL,7,Fwithout any consultation, as policing
OL,8,Ffaces a crisis of public trust and
OL,9,Fconfidence, and as it is about to be
OL,10,Fhanded a much stronger national
OL,11,Fcentre, risks creating a dangerous
OL,12,Faccountability vacuum."
OL,14,FSpurrell, who is also PCC Merseyside,
OL,15,Fsaid having directly-elected PCCs has
OL,16,F"transformed policing accountability".
